 the *sequencing* of karmaphalas and picking o=\r\nf agents for their delivery.\n&gt;&gt; \n&gt;&gt; =C3=82=C2=A0\n&gt;&gt; At any time, some karma=\r\ns from one&#39;s past are placed in a &quot;must experience karmaphala in this life&quot;=\r\n pool, some karmas in a &quot;preferably experience karmaphala in this life&quot; poo=\r\nl and the rest in the third pool which may not be experienced anytime soon.=\r\n The way karmas are assigned and ordered in these pools is based on the bal=\r\nancing of karma/karmaphala sequencing of all beings.\n&gt;&gt; =C3=82=C2=A0\n&gt;&gt; The=\r\n assignment and ordering of these pools will constantly undergo churn as on=\r\ne engages in various new actions and adds them to the pools. Also, as new p=\r\neople enter one&#39;s life, possibilities in terms of karmaphala delivery agent=\r\ns and sequencing may change and hence the pools may be re-arranged.\n&gt;&gt; =C3=\r\n=82=C2=A0\n&gt;&gt; *=C3=82=C2=A0=C3=82=C2=A0=C3=82=C2=A0=C3=82=C2=A0=C3=82=C2=A0=\r\n=C3=82=C2=A0=C3=82=C2=A0 *=C3=82=C2=A0=C3=82=C2=A0=C3=82=C2=A0=C3=82=C2=A0=\r\n=C3=82=C2=A0=C3=82=C2=A0=C3=82=C2=A0 *\n&gt;&gt; =C3=82=C2=A0\n&gt;&gt; As one engages in=\r\n remedial measures such as prayers, fasting, donations etc, one may transfo=\r\nrm one&#39;s nature, change one&#39;s vulnerabilities or re-arrange one&#39;s dynamics =\r\nwith other beings (including planets, deities etc, who are the subtle agent=\r\ns of delivery of karmaphala, who operate through other people who act as ph=\r\nysical agents of delivery!). The karma pools may be re-arranged as a result=\r\n. Some undesirable karmas may be downgraded to a lower pool or pushed down =\r\nin order within the same pool. Or, some desirable karmas may be upgraded to=\r\n a higher pool or pushed up in order within the same pool.\n&gt;&gt; =C3=82=C2=A0W=\r\nhen someone curses or blesses one, with sufficient mental force behind it (=\r\nthis is the key), the same thing can happen. It is all about re-arranging k=\r\narmas between the karmik pools. Every action by one, or even people around =\r\none, has the potential to re-arrange one&#39;s karmik pools. A karma about to g=\r\nive karmaphala may be postponed or a karma that was not to give karmaphala =\r\nanytime soon may be advanced sooner.\n&gt;&gt; =C3=82=C2=A0\n&gt;&gt; However, remember t=\r\nhat the remedial measure has to be as intense as the karma that it is tryin=\r\ng to manipulate. You can move a small rock with small force, but you need a=\r\n large force to move a big rock or a hill.\n&gt;&gt; =C3=82=C2=A0\n&gt;&gt; \n&gt;&gt; If there =\r\nis no negative karma in one&#39;s pool that can give a specific result, nobody =\r\ncan make one experience that result, no matter what ritual one does. Howeve=\r\nr, even great souls have a lot of negative karmas in their optional pool an=\r\nd even evil people have a lot of positive karmas in their optional pool, an=\r\nd hence powerful remedies, curses and blessings can often make some differe=\r\nnce.\n&gt;&gt; =C3=82=C2=A0\n&gt;&gt; This point is well illustrated by the &quot;Guru Charitr=\r\na&quot; story Digamber ji referred in his point (3).\n&gt;&gt; =C3=82=C2=A0\n&gt;&gt; *=C3=82=\r\n=C2=A0=C3=82=C2=A0=C3=82=C2=A0=C3=82=C2=A0=C3=82=C2=A0=C3=82=C2=A0=C3=82=C2=\r\n=A0 *=C3=82=C2=A0=C3=82=C2=A0=C3=82=C2=A0=C3=82=C2=A0=C3=82=C2=A0=C3=82=C2=\r\n=A0=C3=82=C2=A0 *\n&gt;&gt; =C3=82=C2=A0\n&gt;&gt; If one thinks that one can escape the =\r\nfruits of one&#39;s actions, one is mistakened. God is not like us human beings=\r\n, who may show favoritism towards those who praise them or bribe them. The =\r\nHe-aspect of God is a witness to the play of actions and fruits. The She-as=\r\npect of God is the power that impartially and impassionately manages the fi=\r\nne balance and order within this play of actions and fruits. All beings are=\r\n equal in Her eyes, from the lowest of evil persons to the noblest of saint=\r\ns. She administers just and balanced delivery of fruits to actions using av=\r\nailable agents.\n&gt;&gt; =C3=82=C2=A0\n&gt;&gt; The karmas we committed in the past are =\r\nalready in the pipeline and will give their results sooner or later. The be=\r\nst we can do with them, with some effort, is to perhaps reorder them somewh=\r\nat. The most important thing is to not add more serious bad karmas to the p=\r\nipeline now. Simply put, selfish actions and actions that cause pain or har=\r\nm to others are bad karmas and selfless actions and actions that cause plea=\r\nsure or benefit to others are good karmas.\n&gt;&gt; =C3=82=C2=A0\n&gt;&gt; When it comes=\r\n to manipulating the pre-existing pipeline of karmas awaiting karmaphala, t=\r\nhrough conscious effort and current action, yes, it is possible and general=\r\n guidelines are available in shastras, but we can&#39;t be certain about the sp=\r\necific impact of each action. One thing is for sure - remedial measure for =\r\novercoming a karma has to be commensurate with the karma itself.\n&gt;&gt; =C3=82=\r\n=C2=A0\n&gt;&gt; You need only small force to push a cat out of your way, but need=\r\n a large force to push an elephant.\n&gt;&gt; \n&gt;&gt; =C3=82=C2=A0\n&gt;&gt; Best regards,\n&gt;&gt;=\r\n Narasimha\n&gt;&gt; --------\n&gt;&gt; Astrology & Spirituality Resources: http://www.ve=\r\ndicastrologer.org/\n&gt;&gt; --------\n&gt;&gt; =C3=82=C2=A0\n&gt;&gt; \n&gt;&gt; &gt;____________________=\r\n____________\n&gt;&gt; &gt; From: Ajit Krishnan \n&gt;&gt; &gt;To: mailto:vedic-wisdom%40yahoog=\r\nroups.com \n&gt;&gt; &gt;Sent: Tuesday, February 26, 2013 11:29 PM\n&gt;&gt; &gt;Subject: Re: [=\r\nvedic-wisdom] few questions\n&gt;&gt; &gt; \n&gt;&gt; &gt;\n&gt;&gt; &gt;=C3=82=C2=A0 \n&gt;&gt; &gt;Dear=C3=82=C2=\r\n=A0Digamber,\n&gt;&gt; &gt;\n&gt;&gt; &gt;\n&gt;&gt; &gt;When a kingdom had no royal heirs, a special ele=\r\nphant was appointed by the courtiers to randomly pick the next king. Thus, =\r\nit was possible for a beggar to suddenly find himself the king. Whose karma=\r