 anytime soon. The way karmas are assigned an=\r\nd ordered in these pools is based on the balancing of karma/karmaphala sequ=\r\nencing of all beings.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; =C3=82&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; The assignment and order=\r\ning of these pools will constantly undergo churn as one engages in various =\r\nnew actions and adds them to the pools. Also, as new people enter one&#39;s lif=\r\ne, possibilities in terms of karmaphala delivery agents and sequencing may =\r\nchange and hence the pools may be re-arranged.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; =C3=82&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt;=\r\n *=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=82&nbsp;=\r\n=C3=82&nbsp; *=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=82&nbsp;=\r\n=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=82&nbsp; *&lt;BR&gt;&gt; =C3=82&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; As one engages in r=\r\nemedial measures such as prayers,\n fasting, donations etc, one may transfor=\r\nm one&#39;s nature, change one&#39;s vulnerabilities or re-arrange one&#39;s dynamics w=\r\nith other beings (including planets, deities etc, who are the subtle agents=\r\n of delivery of karmaphala, who operate through other people who act as phy=\r\nsical agents of delivery!). The karma pools may be re-arranged as a result.=\r\n Some undesirable karmas may be downgraded to a lower pool or pushed down i=\r\nn order within the same pool. Or, some desirable karmas may be upgraded to =\r\na higher pool or pushed up in order within the same pool.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; =C3=82&nb=\r\nsp;When someone curses or blesses one, with sufficient mental force behind =\r\nit (this is the key), the same thing can happen. It is all about re-arrangi=\r\nng karmas between the karmik pools. Every action by one, or even people aro=\r\nund one, has the potential to re-arrange one&#39;s karmik pools. A karma about =\r\nto give karmaphala may be postponed or a karma that was not to give karmaph=\r\nala anytime soon may be\n advanced sooner.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; =C3=82&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; Howe=\r\nver, remember that the remedial measure has to be as intense as the karma t=\r\nhat it is trying to manipulate. You can move a small rock with small force,=\r\n but you need a large force to move a big rock or a hill.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; =C3=82&nb=\r\nsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; If there is no negative karma in one&#39;s pool that can g=\r\nive a specific result, nobody can make one experience that result, no matte=\r\nr what ritual one does. However, even great souls have a lot of negative ka=\r\nrmas in their optional pool and even evil people have a lot of positive kar=\r\nmas in their optional pool, and hence powerful remedies, curses and blessin=\r\ngs can often make some difference.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; =C3=82&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; This point =\r\nis well illustrated by the &quot;Guru Charitra&quot; story Digamber ji referred in hi=\r\ns point (3).&lt;BR&gt;&gt; =C3=82&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; *=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=82&n=\r\nbsp;=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=82&nbsp; *=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=82&nb=\r\nsp;=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=82&nbsp; *&lt;BR&gt;&gt;\n =\r\n=C3=82&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; If one thinks that one can escape the fruits of one&#39;s =\r\nactions, one is mistakened. God is not like us human beings, who may show f=\r\navoritism towards those who praise them or bribe them. The He-aspect of God=\r\n is a witness to the play of actions and fruits. The She-aspect of God is t=\r\nhe power that impartially and impassionately manages the fine balance and o=\r\nrder within this play of actions and fruits. All beings are equal in Her ey=\r\nes, from the lowest of evil persons to the noblest of saints. She administe=\r\nrs just and balanced delivery of fruits to actions using available agents.&lt;=\r\nBR&gt;&gt; =C3=82&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; The karmas we committed in the past are alread=\r\ny in the pipeline and will give their results sooner or later. The best we =\r\ncan do with them, with some effort, is to perhaps reorder them somewhat. Th=\r\ne most important thing is to not add more serious bad karmas to the pipelin=\r\ne now. Simply put, selfish actions and actions that cause pain or harm to\n =\r\nothers are bad karmas and selfless actions and actions that cause pleasure =\r\nor benefit to others are good karmas.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; =C3=82&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; When it =\r\ncomes to manipulating the pre-existing pipeline of karmas awaiting karmapha=\r\nla, through conscious effort and current action, yes, it is possible and ge=\r\nneral guidelines are available in shastras, but we can&#39;t be certain about t=\r\nhe specific impact of each action. One thing is for sure - remedial measure=\r\n for overcoming a karma has to be commensurate with the karma itself.&lt;BR&gt;&g=\r\nt; =C3=82&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; You need only small force to push a cat out of your=\r\n way, but need a large force to push an elephant.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; =C3=82&n=\r\nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; Best regards,&lt;BR&gt;&gt; Narasimha&lt;BR&gt;&gt; --------&lt;BR&gt;&gt; Astro=\r\nlogy &amp; Spirituality Resources: &lt;A href=3D&quot;http://www.vedicastrologer.or=\r\ng/&quot; rel=3Dnofollow target=3D_blank&gt;http://www.vedicastrologer.org/&lt;/A&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&=\r\ngt; --------&lt;BR&gt;&gt; =C3=82&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt;\n &gt;___________________=\r\n_____________&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; From: Ajit Krishnan &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;To: &lt;A href=3D&quot;=\r\nmailto:vedic-wisdom%40yahoogroups.com&quot; rel=3Dnofollow target=3D_blank ymail=\r\nto=3D&quot;mailto:vedic-wisdom%40yahoogroups.com&quot;&gt;mailto:vedic-wisdom%40yahoogro=\r\nups.com&lt;/A&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;Sent: Tuesday, February 26, 2013 11:29 PM&lt;BR&gt;&gt; =\r\n&gt;Subject: Re: [vedic-wisdom] few questions&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&lt;BR=\r\n&gt;&gt; &gt;=C3=82&nbsp; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;Dear=C3=82&nbsp;Digamber,&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&lt;=\r\nBR&gt;&gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;When a kingdom had no royal heirs, a special eleph=\r\nant was appointed by the courtiers to randomly pick the next 